25:11.125 --> 25:12.125
‐ So,

25:13.167 --> 25:14.707
as I was saying,

25:14.708 --> 25:18.208
you just... have to find peace, you know.

25:19.292 --> 25:22.000
‐ I drove all the way back home to Austin,

25:22.750 --> 25:24.582
and I still woke up here.

25:24.583 --> 25:25.542
‐ That's the way it works.

25:25.543 --> 25:27.249
You know, one time,
I smoked a bunch of crystal

25:27.250 --> 25:29.167
