25:58.709 --> 26:00.958
Oh my God, who was the guy
that was hunting you?

26:02.333 --> 26:03.333
‐ Fuck!

26:11.375 --> 26:12.458
That was Roy.

26:14.042 --> 26:15.458
He was a guest at the wedding.

26:16.208 --> 26:19.417
Abe's dad's cousin,
of the Schlieffen clan.

26:20.625 --> 26:22.374
