why was he trying to kill you?

26:30.833 --> 26:33.500
One night, a very long time ago,

26:35.833 --> 26:37.417
I partied with Roy.

26:38.458 --> 26:40.082
This was back in the early days,

26:40.083 --> 26:41.957
before I'd really
acquainted myself with everyone.

26:41.958 --> 26:42.875
‐ Hey, hey.

26:42.876 --> 26:44.207
I was just feeling
my way through it.

26:44.208 --> 26:45.958
‐ Uh, tuna?
‐ Yes, sir.

26:50.750 --> 26:52.124
‐ I know you know.

26:52.125 --> 26:53.500
But you don't know that I know.

26:53.958 --> 26:54.917
Or do you know?

26:54.918 --> 26:56.791
‐ Do you ever wonder
if people think you're boring.

26:58.458 --> 27:00.167
‐ Are you being a dick to the bartender?

27:01.208 --> 27:02.791
I would like a Moscato, please.

27:02.792 --> 27:03.833
‐ Sure.

27:04.583 --> 27:07.291
‐ "What might have been
and what has been point to one end,

27:07.292 --> 27:08.792
