27:11.292 --> 27:13.625
‐ On second thought, make that
two shots of bourbon, please.

27:23.000 --> 27:25.041
‐ I like your hat.
‐ Of course you do.

27:26.667 --> 27:27.833
Thank you, ma'am.

27:29.208 --> 27:30.249
To the struggle.

27:31.168 --> 27:32.916
Mister and Missus Schlieffen.

27:32.917 --> 27:34.874
