28:05.583 --> 28:08.667
‐ ...money. Um,
but tonight is not about me.

28:10.917 --> 28:12.999
‐ You were right. Got 'em.

28:13.000 --> 28:14.457
I don't know what that was.

28:18.250 --> 28:19.582
‐ Oi, open up, you cunts.

28:19.583 --> 28:21.124
‐ Give me my shit back! Come on!

28:24.625 --> 28:27.166
We're the shit.
We're the shit. We are the shit.

28:27.167 --> 28:29.041
We are the shit.

28:29.042 --> 28:30.332
‐ You're alive!

28:30.333 --> 28:32.249
Oi, come on.
Give me back my pills.

28:42.583 --> 28:43.750
This is

28:45.167 --> 28:49.250
