29:07.708 --> 29:08.916
What is it?

29:08.917 --> 29:11.207
Your ancestors are in there.

29:11.208 --> 29:14.457
‐ My ancestors are in there?

29:14.458 --> 29:18.041
‐ Your answers.
The answers you're looking for.

29:18.042 --> 29:19.499
‐ Okay.

29:19.500 --> 29:22.167
That's a totally different thing, but

29:24.708 --> 29:25.833
I'm in.

29:27.125 --> 29:30.208
You took too much.

29:31.250 --> 29:32.916
No, wait. Roy, wait, wait.

29:34.458 --> 29:36.207
