29:36.208 --> 29:37.750
That was a mistake.

29:38.167 --> 29:41.125
When Roy found out about his new life,
he did not take it lightly.

29:42.167 --> 29:44.374
Luckily, he lives in Irvine
and wakes up there every day,

29:44.375 --> 29:48.332
