you're gonna spend it all today.

30:41.375 --> 30:43.582
‐ You know that's a scam?
‐ Of course. Yeah.

30:43.583 --> 30:45.833
I just like to give back whenever I can.

30:47.125 --> 30:48.957
Material matters don't really concern me.

30:48.958 --> 30:50.499
‐ With the exception of booze and burritos

30:50.500 --> 30:52.082
