31:24.042 --> 31:26.416
‐ I don't think he ever walked again.

31:28.167 --> 31:29.167
Darla.

31:30.125 --> 31:31.957
‐ If you insist.

31:31.958 --> 31:33.957
‐ I bet that was great.
‐ You would have bet right.

31:33.958 --> 31:35.291
‐ What about Tala?
‐ No.

31:35.292 --> 31:36.500
