31:41.042 --> 31:42.208
‐ It's the first dance.

31:43.042 --> 31:44.457
‐ And that's a deal‐breaker?

31:44.458 --> 31:46.416
‐ That didn't work?
‐ It was a big swing.

31:46.417 --> 31:48.207
‐ Right.
