what you're talking about.

33:04.000 --> 33:06.416
We. You. Me. Everyone. Everyone we know.

33:06.417 --> 33:09.249
Nobody can stand the idea

33:09.250 --> 33:10.292
of being alone,

33:11.333 --> 33:15.791
so we... buy into this pageantry

33:15.792 --> 33:18.374
