34:15.917 --> 34:18.833
‐ Actually, just‐‐
Sorry, hold on one second.

34:19.833 --> 34:20.958
You can take that.

34:52.208 --> 34:53.208
Are you joking right now?

35:05.500 --> 35:07.166
All right! Get down!

35:07.167 --> 35:09.167
Get down! Get down!

35:12.167 --> 35:13.541
Down! Hey! Hey!

35:13.542 --> 35:15.332
This place‐‐ Get off me!

35:15.333 --> 35:17.874
