35:32.375 --> 35:33.957
‐ Sister stuff. But I think I'm good.

35:33.958 --> 35:37.041
Selflessness is just... it's fantastic.

35:37.042 --> 35:38.042
‐ Right.

35:39.667 --> 35:42.167
‐ Uh‐oh, Alan, you owe me
a shot of whiskey.

35:44.792 --> 35:45.792
Alan.

35:46.250 --> 35:48.291
Well, Nyles, this has been great.

35:48.292 --> 35:51.207
Well, you know, not great,
but it's been interesting.

35:51.208 --> 35:53.208
And, hey, in all your future loops,

35:53.583 --> 35:57.082
please keep me out of that fucking cave.

35:57.083 --> 36:00.292
And good luck with that psychopath
who keeps trying to murder you.

36:01.292 --> 36:02.707
Thank you.

36:02.708 --> 36:03.583
Deal with him.

36:03.584 --> 36:05.333
‐ Yeah.
‐ That could be your way out.

36:05.917 --> 36:07.666
‐ Well, you seem
to have it all figured out.

36:07.667 --> 36:08.875
‐ Good luck.

36:10.458 --> 36:12.083
Coming!

36:12.500 --> 36:14.082
Oh, Sarah?

36:14.083 --> 36:17.083
‐ Didn't work. Life is meaningless.
Let's get the fuck out of here.

36:18.333 --> 36:19.583
‐ Oh my God.

36:21.458 --> 36:22.541
Are you...

36:22.542 --> 36:23.833
fucking cheating on me?

36:24.792 --> 36:25.792
What?

36:26.458 --> 36:27.667
This isn't funny.

36:28.583 --> 36:29.792
Okay, stop.

36:30.375 --> 36:31.583
I'm serious.

36:31.917 --> 36:33.207
Stop copying me!

36:33.208 --> 36:35.332
Stop pretending like you know everything!

36:38.458 --> 36:40.625
‐ Okay, I'm gonna go.
‐ Wait, what?

36:41.167 --> 36:42.333
‐ And what is this place?

36:42.792 --> 36:45.374
‐ This is kind of a safehouse for me.

36:45.375 --> 36:47.666
The family who lives here is out of town.

36:47.667 --> 36:51.375
I don't know when they're coming back,
but... it's not today.

