Orchid Explosion by Fournier?

57:13.875 --> 57:14.875
‐ Oh my God.

57:15.750 --> 57:16.750
‐ I didn't think so.

57:17.625 --> 57:19.332
‐ Get the fuck out of here, okay.

57:19.333 --> 57:20.999
‐ Abe, let's take a walk.

57:21.000 --> 57:22.416
‐ You don't actually believe
this guy, do you?

57:22.417 --> 57:24.499
‐ You cheated on your fiancée
the night before your wedding

57:24.500 --> 57:25.791
with her sister?

57:25.792 --> 57:27.916
And you know what, fuck all of you.

57:27.917 --> 57:29.416
Sarah's a good person,

57:29.417 --> 57:31.957
but for some reason, she's never been
good enough for any of you‐‐

57:33.125 --> 57:34.166
Hey!

57:34.167 --> 57:36.042
Come here.

57:37.625 --> 57:39.333
‐ Stay back!
‐ What are you doing?

57:41.125 --> 57:43.332
‐ Try to ruin my life, huh?
Come on. Let's go.

57:44.875 --> 57:46.000
Ohh!

57:48.833 --> 57:51.333
‐ Misty's boyfriend!

57:54.500 --> 57:55.458
‐ Oh wow.

57:55.459 --> 57:57.124
‐ Oh my God, oh my God!

57:57.125 --> 57:59.082
