58:55.000 --> 58:56.292
‐ I miss her, Jerry.

58:57.083 --> 58:58.083
Who?

58:59.792 --> 59:02.208
‐ Sarah.
‐ Wilder?

59:03.542 --> 59:04.542
Oh.

59:05.083 --> 59:06.708
