59:14.458 --> 59:15.542
‐ I love her.

59:18.375 --> 59:19.375
‐ I see.

59:21.083 --> 59:22.249
That's interesting.

59:30.167 --> 59:31.416
Wake up.

59:56.208 --> 59:57.750
Roy!

59:58.417 --> 01:00:00.042
