01:00:02.708 --> 01:00:04.124
‐ Motherfucker.

01:00:04.125 --> 01:00:06.457
‐ You were right, it's dark down here!

01:00:06.458 --> 01:00:07.957
‐ What the fuck are you doing here?

01:00:07.958 --> 01:00:09.416
‐ Hey, Roy.

01:00:09.417 --> 01:00:11.750
