‐ Thank you.
You have beautiful skin.

01:12:36.833 --> 01:12:39.000
I love your haircut.
‐ Me too.

01:12:39.417 --> 01:12:41.207
Without further ado,
let me bring up

01:12:41.208 --> 01:12:43.082
